{"word":"πυκνότης","slug":"πυκνότης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πυκνότης</b></el> <el>(πυκνότης, ητος, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πυκνός</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>closeness, thickness, denseness</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>frequency</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>sagacity, shrewdness, craft</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}